Problem Link:-
https://www.codingninjas.com/studio/problems/n-to-1-without-loop_8357243?utm_source=striver&utm_medium=website&utm_campaign=a_zcoursetuf




Solution:-
    public static int[] Nto1(int x,int arr[])
    {
        if(x==0)
        return arr;


        arr[arr.length-x] = x;

        Nto1(x-1, arr);

        return arr;
    }
